                 obo:IAO_0000115 "A unique individual identifier is an identifier that is unique for one individual of a class. Unique individual identifiers follow usually a structure defined e.g. by a sector division." ;
                 rdfs:label "unique individual identifier"@en ;
                 oeo:OEO_00020426 """issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/461
pull request: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/523""" ;
                 rdfs:subPropertyOf dc:identifier .


