   owl:annotatedTarget "It is possible that this relation should be a functional property, that is for all x, y, z if x describes y and x describes z then y = z. For example, if a financial report x describes the quarterly results of a company y and that same financial report describes the quarterly results of a company z, then it should be inferred that companies y and z are the same. We refrained from classifying the relation as a functional property on the concern that descriptions are multifaceted and so consequently it may be that the same report would contain descriptions of multiple entities."@en ;
   prov:wasDerivedFrom <https://openenergyplatform.org/ontology/oeo/releases/2.9.0/imports/cco-extracted.owl>
 ] .

