#################################################################

###  http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#topDataProperty
owl:topDataProperty rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .


###  https://openenergyplatform.org/ontology/oeo/OEO_00020440
oeo:OEO_00020440 rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
                 rdfs:subPropertyOf owl:topDataProperty ;
                 rdfs:domain oeo:OEO_00000365 ;
                 rdfs:range xsd:dateTime ;
                 obo:IAO_0000115 "Has scenario year value is a relation between a scenario factsheet and a xsd:dateTime value." ;
                 rdfs:comment "This data property allows for comparable and sortable annotation of scenario years in the OEKG." ;
                 rdfs:label "has scenario year value"@en ;
                 oeo:OEO_00020426 """add
issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/2035
pull request: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/2045""" .


###  https://openenergyplatform.org/ontology/oeo/OEO_00140170
