obo:UO_0000000 rdf:type owl:Class ;
               owl:equivalentClass oeo:OEO_00010490 ;
               obo:IAO_0000115 "\"A unit of measurement is a standardized quantity of a physical quality.\" [Wikipedia:Wikipedia]" ;
               obo:IAO_0000118 "unit of measurement"@en ;
               rdfs:isDefinedBy obo:uo.owl ;
               rdfs:label "unit" ;
               oeo:OEO_00020426 """issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/533
pull request: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/537
renaming
pull request: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/895
Remove unintended duplicated SubClassOf axiom and restore OEO definition:
https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/1741
Delete SubClassOf axiom, add EquivalentTo axiom and restore definition from UO:
