                 obo:IAO_0000115 "Process climate neutrality is a process attribute that conforms to some climate neutrality criteria."@en ;
                 rdfs:label "process climate neutrality"@en ;
                 oeo:OEO_00020425 "study descriptor tag" ;
                 oeo:OEO_00020426 """issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/1392
pull request: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/1722

add oekg annotation
issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/2063
pull request: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/2065""" .


