   owl:annotatedProperty skos:definition ;
   owl:annotatedTarget "A Stasis of Specifically Dependent Continuant in which some Independent Continuant bears a Quality or Realizable Entity that has suffered impairment (i.e., a decrease or loss) due to a previous action or event such that the Independent Continuant is now of lesser value, usefulness, or functionality."@en ;
   prov:wasDerivedFrom <https://openenergyplatform.org/ontology/oeo/releases/2.9.0/imports/cco-extracted.owl>
 ] .

