   owl:annotatedProperty skos:scopeNote ;
   owl:annotatedTarget "This class can be used to instantiate instances that might otherwise be treated by defined classes such as Damaged Vehicle or Wounded Person. The Independent Continuant and Quality or Realizable Entity are participants of the stasis which can in turn be related to the temporal interval via the occurs on property. "@en ;
   prov:wasDerivedFrom <https://openenergyplatform.org/ontology/oeo/releases/2.9.0/imports/cco-extracted.owl>
 ] .

