                 oeo:OEO_00000504 oeo:OEO_00000242 ;
                 obo:IAO_0000115 """The CRF sector (IPCC 2006) 'fuel combustion' is a sector defined by the 2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories:
Emissions from the intentional oxidation of materials within an apparatus that is designed to raise heat and provide it either as heat or as mechanical work to a process or for use away from the apparatus.""" ;
                 obo:IAO_0000119 "2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories, Volume 2, Chapter 2.2, https://www.ipcc-nggip.iges.or.jp/public/2006gl/" ;
                 rdfs:label "CRF sector (IPCC 2006): fuel combustion"@en ;
                 oeo:OEO_00010037 "CRF 1.A" ;
                 oeo:OEO_00020426 """issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/461
