                 obo:IAO_0000115 """The CRF sector (IPCC 2006) 'energy industry' is an energy transformation sector defined by the 2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories:
Comprises emissions from fuels combusted by the fuel extraction or energy-producing industries.""" ;
                 obo:IAO_0000119 "2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories, Volume 2, Chapter 2.2, https://www.ipcc-nggip.iges.or.jp/public/2006gl/" ;
