                 oeo:OEO_00000504 oeo:OEO_00000242 ;
                 obo:IAO_0000115 """The CRF sector (IPCC 2006) 'transport' is a transport sector defined by the 2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories:
Emissions from the combustion and evaporation of fuel for all transport activity (excluding military transport), regardless of the sector, specified by sub-categories below. Emissions from fuel sold to any air or marine vessel engaged in international transport (1 A 3 a i and 1 A 3 d i) should as far as possible be excluded from the totals and subtotals in this category and should be reported separately.""" ;
                 obo:IAO_0000119 "2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories, Volume 2, Chapter 3.1, https://www.ipcc-nggip.iges.or.jp/public/2006gl/" ;
                 rdfs:label "CRF sector (IPCC 2006): transport"@en ;
                 oeo:OEO_00010037 "CRF 1.A.3" ;
                 oeo:OEO_00020426 """issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/461
pull request: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/523

