                 obo:IAO_0000115 """The CRF sector (IPCC 2006) 'other transportation' is a transport sector defined by the 2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories:
Combustion emissions from all remaining transport activities including pipeline transportation, ground activities in airports and harbours, and off-road activities not otherwise reported under 1 A 4 c Agriculture or 1 A 2. Manufacturing Industries and Construction. Military transport should be reported under 1 A 5.""" ;
                 obo:IAO_0000119 "2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories, Volume 1, Chapter 8.5, https://www.ipcc-nggip.iges.or.jp/public/2006gl/" ;
                 rdfs:label "CRF sector (IPCC 2006): other transportation"@en ;
                 oeo:OEO_00010037 "CRF 1.A.3.e" ;
