                 obo:IAO_0000115 """The CRF sector (IPCC 2006) 'settlements' is an agriculture, forestry and land use sector defined by the 2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories:
Emissions and removals from all developed land, including transportation infrastructure and human settlements of any size, unless they are already included under other categories.""" ;
                 obo:IAO_0000119 "2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories, Volume 1, Chapter 8.5, https://www.ipcc-nggip.iges.or.jp/public/2006gl/" ;
                 rdfs:label "CRF sector (IPCC 2006): settlements"@en ;
                 oeo:OEO_00010037 "CRF 4.E" ;
                 oeo:OEO_00020426 """issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/858
