                          oeo:OEO_00000227 ;
                 obo:BFO_0000050 oeo:OEO_00010172 ;
                 oeo:OEO_00000504 oeo:OEO_00000242 ;
                 obo:IAO_0000115 """The CRF sector (IPCC 2006) 'electrical equipment' is an industry sector defined by the 2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories:
Electrical equipment is used in the transmission and distribution of electricity above 1 kV. SF6 is used in gasinsulated switchgear (GIS), gas circuit breakers (GCB), gas-insulated transformers (GIT), gas-insulated lines (GIL), outdoor gas-insulated instrument transformers, reclosers, switches, ring main units and other equipment.""" ;
                 obo:IAO_0000119 "2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories, Volume 1, Chapter 8.5, https://www.ipcc-nggip.iges.or.jp/public/2006gl/" ;
                 rdfs:label "CRF sector (IPCC 2006): electrical equipment"@en ;
                 oeo:OEO_00010037 "CRF 2.G.1" ;
                 oeo:OEO_00020426 """issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/1401
